    p ALC “Perechin Timber and Chemical Plant” has been FSC certified since 2006.
    p It was the first enterprise in the region and one of the firsts in Ukraine.
    p During the certification time, more than 12 years the company did a lot to promote FSC values in Ukraine, resulting forest enterprises to implement FSC system for Ukrainian forests; as well in Europe, by promoting FSC products at the early beginning of FSC establishing.
    p Plant fully respects the FSC values and follows its policy.
    p The certificate of the ALC “Perechin Timber and Chemical Plant” was suspended in February 2019 and was terminated in June 2019.
    p.font-weight-bold We would like to inform all our Stakeholders - ALC “Perechin Timber and Chemical Plant” has never sold uncertified charcoal with FSC label and the plant is open for audits by certification bodies.
    p Since the suspension of the certificate, our team is in negotiations with FSC about terms of renewal of our certificate and to sign Memorandum of Understanding.
    p Despite the fact of our suspension and further termination, the plant has never stopped to buy FSC raw material and to promote FSC values.
    p.font-weight-bold Sustainable forest management is the main value of the ALC “Perechin Timber and Chemical Plant”.

